    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.4.19"/>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">IN THE HEART OF THE ROCKIES                                                                                         ENOS MILLS
                                        WITH THE PINES, BIRDS                                                                                   LONGS PEAK, ESTES PARK
                                            AND WILD FLOWERS                                                                                            COLORADO

                                                                                    LONG'S PEAK INN</hi>
                </fw>
                
                                                                                                                    <fw type="curatorial">19</fw>

                <opener>                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                    <dateline>May 1, 1916.</dateline>

                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Mr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt,</addrLine>
                            <addrLine>Bancroft, Nebraska.</addrLine>
                    </address>

                    <salute>My dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>With intense interest I have read your <title>Song of Hugh Glass</title>. At times in this story you reach splendid poetic heights. It is a splendid contribution to the heroic literature of this country. I congratulate you for this magnificent production and I thank you for all the hard and faithful work that you have put upon it.</p>
    
                <p>I am hammering away as usual and will have another little book out mid-summer. Possibly another one late autumn.</p>
    
                <p>Trusting that all goes to your liking,</p>

                <p>I am</p>
                <closer>
                                                    <salute>Sincerely yours,</salute>

                                                        <signed>Enos Mills</signed>
                                                        
                                                        <note>[a naturalist]</note>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
